Package org.galiosten.calculator.operation

Provides the classes required to evaluate each node in the expression tree.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Add
    The Add operation represents the addition of its operands.
    BinaryOperation
    Base class for binary operations.
    Div
    The Div operation represents the expression numerator / denominator where the first operand is the numerator and the second operand is the denominator.
    Identity
    The Identity operation is a special case operation that models single Integer values in a way that can be evaluated as any other model.
    Mult
    The Mult operation represents the multiplication of its operands.
    Operation
    Abstract base class for all operations.
    Sub
    The Sub operation represents the subtraction of the second operand from the first.

Package org.galiosten.calculator.operation Description

Provides the classes required to evaluate each node in the expression tree.
